{"tid":650581,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"請問這裡有無負責人?","createTime":"2018-05-02T12:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T09:35:29.000Z","uid":16970,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73227ae036147eb2bcecb4f37d0672c927454b94","tid":650581,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:54:30.000Z","msg":"想問連登負責管理嘅人係咪諗住無為而治, 乜都唔理, 由得個論壇自己run?<br />\n<br />\n站務台咁多post, 鍾意就抽一兩個答, 平時就潛晒水, 由得啲人晌度嘈交, 咁要個站務台嚟做咩?<br />\n<br />\n吹水台有條友叫9527, 成日晌人貼女相果陣無端端貼一位唔知係乜水女性嘅照片, 貼足幾個月, admin理都唔理下, 搞乜?<br />\n<br />\n有人晌時事台玩起底, 貼咗講嘢唔啱心水版友嘅相出嚟, 得閒就拎出嚟貼下, admin又係理都唔理下, 又係搞乜?<br />\n<br />\n係咪搞個論壇, 然後由得啲人自己嘈到拆天, 咁就係好事?"},{"pid":"4d0389b8a669d52912f3b24d2b03a0c9c19a297c","tid":650581,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"係囉 之前有人洗版都唔理"},{"pid":"8887262ef4e3eab573a9ba998ba264854a0ff88d","tid":650581,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"唔係潮文負皮"},{"pid":"b3b229826807ed0ac51cba57057fe1059297f17d","tid":650581,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06a1b2a85a9ac4068d1af172bf84634dfccef09f","tid":650581,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:28:53.000Z","msg":"又係冇人覆, 係勁嘅."},{"pid":"f1eeb4ba73353ed55ebb5f6125e5945a30c480d5","tid":650581,"uid":59440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449d851723fed14e54a78839d7e6699466fe1196","tid":650581,"uid":153442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:57:52.000Z","msg":"有冇link睇下乜事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd917bca2ac7e0dba10d1030ec4132739b6f5264","tid":650581,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449d851723fed14e54a78839d7e6699466fe119